%% SC-01 · 拍照录入错题 · owner=[s7, s3] · mockup=P03
flowchart TD
  Start([用户在首页]) --> FAB[点击拍照 FAB]
  FAB --> Choose{选择来源}
  Choose -->|相机| Camera[P03 相机预览]
  Choose -->|相册| Album[选相册]
  Choose -->|手动| Manual[P03 手动输入题干]
  Camera --> Preview[预览+裁剪]
  Album --> Preview
  Preview --> Compress{大小检查}
  Compress -->|≤ 10MB| Upload[PUT OSS presign url]
  Compress -->|> 10MB| ErrSize[错误 413 · 提示重选]
  ErrSize --> Choose
  Upload --> UploadOK{PUT 成功?}
  UploadOK -->|200-299| Submit[POST /wrongbook/items]
  UploadOK -->|失败| ErrNet[提示网络错误 · 重试]
  ErrNet --> Upload
  Manual --> Submit
  Submit --> SubmitOK{201 OK?}
  SubmitOK -->|是| Jump[跳 P04 Analyzing]
  SubmitOK -->|否| ErrSubmit[显示错误 · 重试]
  ErrSubmit --> Submit
